# CODEOWNERS

# Format: <path or pattern> <@user or @team>
# - Patterns are matched top-to-bottom; first match wins
# - Add specific paths before broad patterns
# - @teams can be GitHub teams in the org

# Default owner for all code
* @cochranblock

# Root-level config and CI
/.github/          @cochranblock @devops-team
/Cargo.toml        @cochranblock
